The paper discusses the conflicts between GDPR regulations and the design, architecture, and operation of modern systems, which involves aspects of cybersecurity (cs.CR), software engineering (cs.SE), cyber law and policy (cs.CY), database systems (cs.DB), and machine learning (cs.LG) in terms of making unexplainable decisions.
